<tr class='tr-assignment'>
<td class='td-assignment-name large-12 medium-12 small-36'>
<h3><a href="/cohorts/37/assignments/989">Object Oriented Programming</a></h3>
</td>
<td class='large-22 td-assignment-summary medium-12 small-36'>Ruby is pure object-oriented language and everything appears to Ruby, as an object. Every value in Ruby is an object, even the most primitive things: strings, numbers and even true and false. Even a class itself is an object that is an instance of the Class class. This assignment will take you through all the major functionalities related to Object Oriented Ruby.</td>
